        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Right to Remain Safe Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill generally requires a local government to certify that its municipal police department has not been defunded in order to be eligible for grant funding from the Department of Justice.</p>]]>
        </text>
